{"tid":1754516,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有一年輪到立法會，準備定投票策略","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T13:52:42.000Z","uid":88263,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf990c6ccadad6b024c10abf9fb127ffc9648ec","tid":1754516,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"如果出年仲未支爆，立法會選舉應該都係同一個玩法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/education/files/chinese/Exhibition_Panels_Supplementary_Notes/Composition-of-the-LegCo.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Ffiles%2Fchinese%2FExhibition_Panels_Supplementary_Notes%2FComposition-of-the-LegCo.pdf&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJj44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=383df8a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/education/files/chinese/Exhibition_Panels_Supplementary_Notes/Composition-of-the-LegCo.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n睇返上屆立法會直選議席<br />\n港島：6<br />\n九西：6<br />\n九東：5<br />\n新西：9<br />\n新東：9<br />\n<br />\n2016嗰次直選個派彩好似係<br />\n港島：3<br />\n九西：4<br />\n九東：2<br />\n新西：4<br />\n新東：7<br />\n<br />\n想keep 返咁多個議席嘅就約好咁多個fd/屋企人分散投幾個民主陣營嘅人<br />\n例如話：港島要3席，<br />\n一家三口就分投3個民主陣營；<br />\n約朋友嘅，首先要確定自己真係帶眼識人，個fd 同真係好fd，咁就約定3個fd 分開投3個民主陣營，再同第4個fd 講，叫佢搵多2個其他真係好fd嘅fd 分散投，切記唔可以重複約投。<br />\n<br />\n如果屋企人係搖擺賓洲中間派嘅，咁哩一年就加多兩錢肉緊渡佢一齊投<br />\n如果屋企人真投票意向不明確嘅，就出年自己去少次旅行，請屋企人去旅行盡下孝心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊一年大家都參加多啲蛇齊餅傻，去撚鳩保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80152afb343e038ea192e180dc1e4e97653f81f","tid":1754516,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"仲有要轉去傳統功能界别<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb761f28f94daaf66db561f9ce6982c36b5d8a1","tid":1754516,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"人人睇下合唔合乎資格<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/FC.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2FFC.htm&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJj44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=771d79c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/FC.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dba256da05bcd5ebed6bd0ed6a3a1f95fc93fa7a","tid":1754516,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:53:08.000Z","msg":"功能一定要搞，唔可以再自動當選"},{"pid":"ba0ed7801e79db8b374e7272df0ef5e5283eabf2","tid":1754516,"uid":332362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:55:05.000Z","msg":"比例代表制嘅係選名單 而最大弱點係可用 Dilute 方法去冲淡敵方名單票數"},{"pid":"a3ffa4609cff731117e7fe88186de9be51f7552a","tid":1754516,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"自己夾，不如用細區分<br />\n根據今次區議會投票統計，每區集中投其中一個咁"},{"pid":"b1fb4e23961fa787b569557a2a5e0f6c1b1659c1","tid":1754516,"uid":72431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"生日月份投票法有無得諗"},{"pid":"ac4a7d8ef8ca83f379e263349c36b79f9bbe3e23","tid":1754516,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"或者地方投票法<br />\n太子-a<br />\n藍田-b<br />\nD票數數到"},{"pid":"b434154bd63210aa4752e0a8c160c17f0edc10f7","tid":1754516,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:00:11.000Z","msg":"可唔可以研究下隨機投票法 用大數法則最穩陣 前提要統一"},{"pid":"cb1128ba038a5a9185d7f18f59c74fb66b273f90","tid":1754516,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:00:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以留意下離島<br />\n大嶼山T01 選區余漢坤區議員連任成功<br />\n佢呢屆在任有做過以下嘅事:<br />\n<br />\n<strong>佢有份提名林鄭月娥<br />\n有份和議明日大嶼願景<br />\n支持一地兩檢</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔睇實呢個人，出年可能過埋一兆人工島<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/person/8a3e7299-bed2-476d-85d8-c43bf1a38f32/%E4%BD